Package: smglr
Title: Stress based layouts for network visualization
Version: 0.0.5.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Schoch", email = "david.schoch@manchester.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package implements several new deterministic layout algorithms to visualize networks. Most are based on the concept of stress majorization.
URL: https://github.com/schochastics/smglr
BugReports: https://github.com/schochastics/smglr/issues
